California T
HANDLING U SP
California dreaming from $762 per week
Realise your dream of owning a Ferrari today with an unrivalled offer from Ferrari Brisbane. Enjoy sportiness, versatility and
signature Ferrari driving pleasure with the California T - Ferrari's front-engined V8 with retractable hard top. Also available
with the Handling Speciale package, featuring stiffer handling and deeper exhaust sound.
Year Model
Features
Kms
2015 Ferrari California T
Classic Rosso Corsa over Beige Tradizione, 20" Matt Grigio Corsa Forged Alloy Wheels, Apple CarPlay 15,500
2016 Ferrari California T Handling Speciale Rosso Corsa with Nero DS Roof, Handling Speciale Package, 20" Diamond Finished Forged Alloy Wheels 4,900
2016 Ferrari California T Handling Speciale Giallo Modena with Nero Roof, Handling Speciale Package, 20"Glossy Black Forged Alloy Wheels 3,021
Drive Away"
from $762 per week with a $119,997 deposit"
from $960 per week with a $143,997 deposit
from $940 per week with a $140,997 deposit"
*The manufacturer's recommended drive away price for Ferrari California T models ordered and delivered by 31.07.2017. While stocks last. Cannot be combined with any other offer. Excludes fleet, government & rental buyers. Fees, charges, terms,
conditions & approval criteria apply. Consult Ferrari Brisbane for further details. From ALPHERA Financial services (a division of BMW Australia Finance Ltd, Australian credit licence 392387) while stocks last on a commercial loan over 36 months at
5.99% interest p.a. On a drive away price of the vehicle with sequential automatic transmission and no optional extras of (1) $379990, (2) $479990 and (3) $469990, with monthly repayments of (1) $3298.92, (2) $4156.85 and (3) $4071.05 and a
final payment of (1) $199995, (2) $249995 and (3) $234995. Total amount payable at the end of the contract is (1) $422754, (2) $533639 and (3) $522550. No other offers apply. Fleet, government & rental buyers excluded. PPSR fees payable by
client. Fees, charges, terms & conditions apply. Offer applies at Ferrari Brisbane while stocks last on listed vehicles ordered & delivered by 31st July, 2017. Offer is subject to ALPHERA Financial Services normal lending and approval criteria. This offer does
not take into account your personal circumstances & you should seek independent legal and financial advice for your specific circumstances. ALPHERA Financial Services reserves the right to change or extend the offer. Different terms, fees or other loan
amounts might result in a different comparison rate. For further details contact Ferrari Brisbane.
OFFICIAL FERRARI DEALER
Ferrari Brisbane
Corner Breakfast Creek Road & Waterloo Street, Newstead 4006. Entrance via Cunningham Street.
Tel. 07 3853 0125 sales@ferraribrisbane.com | ferraribrisbane.com.au
